od, but that is not it.\u201d They said, \u201cCharity.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIt is good,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3657,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/13\/umar-ibn-abdul-aziz-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":33359,"position":4},"title":"Umar II on Faith: Islam is fulfilled by duties, limits, traditions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bukhari reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cVerily, faith consists of obligations, laws, limits, and traditions. Whoever perfects them has perfected faith, and whoever does not perfect them will not have perfect faith.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1\/11 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34473,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/19\/islam-eight-types-of-good\/","url_meta":{"origin":33359,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Islam: The religion has eight types of good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 19, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIslam has eight shares: Islam is a share, p